title: Recruitment firm Cynet slammed after job posting seeks 'preferably Caucasian' candidate - NBC News
description: Cynet Systems, based in Virginia, posted a job listing on LinkedIn seeking a candidate for a technology job who was "preferably Caucasian."

title: Mayor Pete Assault Accuser: This Was All a 'Despicable' Set-Up - The Daily Beast
description: Michigan college student Hunter Kelly says smear merchants Jacob Wohl and Jack Burkman tricked him into being part of a hoax.
